---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Yihazi" 
  description="Yihazi's ultimate commitment to your data privacy." 
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-12 text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
      
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Commitment</h1>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">1. Zero Upload Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Whether it's sensitive text, image compression, or password generation—all algorithms are strictly executed locally within your browser. <strong>No input data is ever uploaded to any servers.</strong></p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">2. Cookies and Storage</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We safely preserve your language and routing preferences utilizing only <strong>localStorage</strong> APIs. Nothing is used for targeted ads or profiling. We don't embed malicious tracking cookies.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">3. Third-party Links</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">This guarantee strictly covers our active application. Clicking external references embedded inside components defaults you to the respective party's policy framework.</p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
